headline: Humana (HUM): Buy, Sell, or Hold Post Q4 Earnings?
summary: Over the past six months, Humana’s shares (currently trading at $268.69) have posted a disappointing 15.2% loss while the S&P 500 was down 1.4%. This might have investors contemplating their next move.
